and cupped them...

01:38:25.420 --> 01:38:27.260
under her cheek.

01:38:29.060 --> 01:38:31.180
l opened her eyes and--

01:38:33.540 --> 01:38:35.060
and then...

01:38:36.100 --> 01:38:38.020
